        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="T48n2025-start">
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:02:29.968+09:00">夫学般若菩薩、先当起大悲心、発弘誓願、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:04:01.923+09:00">精修三昧、誓度衆生、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:04:59.317+09:00">不為一身独求解脱爾。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:39:01.993+09:00">乃放捨諸緑、休息万事、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:39:25.637+09:00">身心一如、動静無間、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:40:41.044+09:00">其飲食、不多不少、調其睡眠、不節不恣。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:22:27.895+09:00">欲坐禅時、於閑静処、厚敷坐物、寛繋衣帯、令威儀斉整、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:26:40.372+09:00">然後結跏趺坐。先以右足安左陛上、左足安右陛上。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:42:49.187+09:00">或半跏趺坐亦可、但以左足圧右足而已。次以右手安左足上、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:35:25.575+09:00">左掌安右掌上、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-24T13:46:27.624+09:00">両手大拇指面相拄、徐徐挙身前欠、復左右揺振、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-24T13:51:15.432+09:00">乃正身端坐。不得左傾右側前躬後仰、令腰脊頭項骨節相拄、状如浮屠。又不得聳身太過、令人気急不安。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s13" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-24T14:03:50.609+09:00">要令耳与肩対、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-24T14:07:41.494+09:00">鼻与臍対、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-24T14:11:43.559+09:00">舌拄上腭、唇歯相著、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s16" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T09:57:04.762+09:00">目須微開、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s17" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T09:57:36.829+09:00">免致昏睡。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T09:58:03.781+09:00">若得禅定、其力最勝。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:37:27.509+09:00">古有習定高僧、坐常開目。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:38:55.983+09:00">向法雲円通禅師、亦詞人閉目坐禅。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:39:09.571+09:00">以謂黒山鬼窟。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:42:02.896+09:00">蓋有深旨、達者知焉。身相既定、気息既調、然後寛放謄腹、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:45:49.06+09:00">一切善悪、都莫思量。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:49:06.381+09:00">念起即覚、覚之即失。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:50:07.638+09:00">久久忘縁、自成一片、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s27" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:50:24.181+09:00">此坐禅之要術也。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s29" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:55:15.017+09:00">而人多致疾者、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s30" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:56:02.47+09:00">蓋不善用心故也。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-04-01T10:58:23.174+09:00">窺謂坐禅乃安楽法門、</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
